        "question": "<p>(a) Two functions p and q are defined on the set of real numbers, R, by p : y \\(\\to\\) 2y +3 and q : y -&gt; y - 2. Find QOP</p><p>(b) How many four digits odd numbers greater than 4000 can be formed from 1,7,3,8,2 if repetition is allowed?</p>",
