        "question": "<p>Evaluate; \\(\\int^3_1(3x - 2)^5 dx\\)</p>",
        "answer": "<p>\\(\\int^3_1(3x - 2)^5 dx\\)</p><p>Let u = 3x - 2</p><p>\\(\\frac{du}{dx}\\) = 3</p><p>dx = \\(\\frac{dy}{3}\\)</p><p>\\(\\int^3_1(3x - 2)^5 dx\\) = \\(\\int^7_1 \\frac{u^5}{3} du\\)</p><p>= \\(\\frac{u^{5 + 1}}{3(5 + 1)}|^7_1\\) </p><p>= \\(\\frac{u^5}{18}|^7_1\\)</p><p>= \\(\\frac{7^6}{18} = \\frac{1^6}{18}\\)</p><p>= \\(\\frac{7^6 - 1}{18}\\) </p><p>= \\(\\frac{117649}{18}\\)</p><p>= 6536</p>",
        "type": "theory"
    },
