        "question": "<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:500px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>Marks</td>\n<td>10 - 19</td>\n<td>20 - 29</td>\n<td>30 - 39</td>\n<td>40 - 49</td>\n<td>50 - 59</td>\n<td>60 - 69</td>\n<td>70 - 79</td>\n<td>80 - 89</td>\n<td>90 - 99</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Frequency </td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>13</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>12</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>4</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><p>The table shows the distribution of marks scored by 64 students in a test</p><p>(a) Draw a histogram for the distribution.</p><p>(b) Use the histogram to estimate the modal score.</p>",
