        "answer": "<p>F\\(_1\\) = (10N, 090\\(^o\\)), F\\(_2\\) = (20N, 210\\(^o\\))</p><p>F\\(_3\\) = (4N, 33\\(^o\\))</p><p><img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/p206x206/240655664_425603192228106_8384467034316991621_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=aee45a&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGSZ6nlz0vtDsrSiT4Ixvew_iS3zV_ttkT-JLfNX-22REs-MUyw6v_ng9Og9sOY5TBDfZ6SexqLgV10B7o45cOH&amp;_nc_ohc=i2b65vLK9bwAX9XNFAq&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.xx&amp;oh=dbea4a71db4088df2fb8f3342134f5d6&amp;oe=614EC2CF\"></p><p>F\\(_3\\) component x - axis </p><p>= - 4 cos 60\\(^o\\)  = - 2N</p><p>F\\(_2\\) along y - axis</p><p>= 20 x cos 30\\(^o\\) = -1.7320</p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/p206x206/240639950_272815077654648_4155969325345267960_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=aee45a&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEn29CVe146PvLTK-NSsLxkWpQ-GdAsMDpalD4Z0CwwOlItqYzTRmKvzvvnIE-wBoVYMRnpGPYS5H63u469OTKp&amp;_nc_ohc=On8nzd5LS2QAX8stRxA&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.xx&amp;oh=1cefcd04c7930f130dbf20c08584a700&amp;oe=614DDD9B\"></p><p>\\(\\frac{8N}{-1.732N}\\)</p><p>Resultant force</p><p>= \\(\\sqrt{8^2 + (-1.732)^2}\\)</p><p>= \\(\\sqrt{65.999}\\)</p><p>= 8.185N</p><p>= 8.2N</p><p> </p>",
