        "question": "<p>The essays of 10 candidates were ranked by three examiners as shown in the table.</p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:500px\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>candidates</td>\n<td>A</td>\n<td>B</td>\n<td>C</td>\n<td>D</td>\n<td>E</td>\n<td>F</td>\n<td>G</td>\n<td>H</td>\n<td>I</td>\n<td>J</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Examiner I</td>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td>5th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Examiner II</td>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>6th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Examiner III</td>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>10th</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table><p> </p><p>a) Calculate the Spearman's rank correlation coefficient of the ranks assigned by:</p><p>(i) Examiners I and lI;</p><p>(ii) Examiners I and III</p><p>(iii) Examiners II and II.</p><p>(b) Using the results in (a), state which two examiners agree most.</p><p> </p>",
        "answer": "<p>(a)(i)</p><p><img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/p206x206/240779552_528542294925085_2095985458128044909_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=aee45a&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGeyAUaKEba-FmPVzR8gGsi9X74ya24Srf1fvjJrbhKt8vlyZiugshPVYrWabGk6uNxidO1fwbE3JaLT0MdGwvd&amp;_nc_ohc=jnepuBwcsewAX-fC5Ki&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.xx&amp;oh=7d2b33300406fc0ef8d94f46fba118a5&amp;oe=614F9545\"></p><p>Rank coefficient = I = \\(\\frac{6\\sum d^2}{n(n^2 - 1)}\\)</p><p>= 1 - \\(\\frac{6(141)}{10(10^2 - 1)}\\)</p><p>= 1 - \\(\\frac{6(141)}{10 \\times 99}\\)</p><p>= 1 - \\(\\frac{846}{990}\\)</p><p>= 1 - 0.85</p><p>= 0.15</p><p> </p><p>(ii) </p><p><img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/p206x206/240650903_315369210385231_1594786420214710651_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=aee45a&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGgzHUOrDUg0V3TCzkodUQj4KqZPi2Kwafgqpk-LYrBp7E3SSixBM07QCU1FlEOZhvAn-IyFVQLsUTCmSdrCQ8s&amp;_nc_ohc=xYecfZPEqN0AX_qCDOT&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.xx&amp;oh=a1c782121c1d6bb9b38e18f9e56a411b&amp;oe=614EF0EC\"></p><p>Rank coefficient = 1 - \\(\\frac{6(78)}{10(10^2 - 1)}\\)</p><p>= 1 - \\(\\frac{468}{990}\\)</p><p>= 1 - 0.472</p><p>= 0.53</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>(iii) </p><p> </p><p><img src=\"https://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.15752-9/p206x206/240670935_919706522221448_2711644357531427020_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;ccb=1-5&amp;_nc_sid=aee45a&amp;_nc_eui2=AeGkfB8sgtwvdqvf1Dh4-7C75vV7ulO-9pXm9Xu6U772ldOylxbHEpcHdA5iT4YH9APbM1LEyNrH3w-3LE8iFShn&amp;_nc_ohc=NrudO3YOs-oAX_TUAWK&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.xx&amp;oh=3a0cdde1fe7deeb3541175de54930a07&amp;oe=614E6BB9\"></p><p> </p><p>Rank coefficient = 1 - \\(\\frac{6(78)}{10(10^2 - 1)}\\)</p><p>= 0.53</p><p> </p><p>(b) Examiner II and III</p>",
